Cook ancient grains according to package directions. Rinse under cold water; let drain. Meanwhile, combine cucumber, parsley, onions and mint in large bowl. Combine lemon juice, salt, pepper and olive oil in 1-cup glass measuring cup. Add grains to cucumber mixture; mix well. Pour lemon juice mixture over all; toss to coat. Stir in shrimp. Line platter with lettuce; spoon tabouli in center.